Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:05:01.77,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Let's see if this mansion and this \Nkid are really good enough for you.}Vậy thì tôi sẽ kiểm tra coi nó có xứng với cô không.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.45,0:05:07.73,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{I'm going to watch for a while to see if \Nyou're really cut out to be Lilith's master,}Tôi sẽ theo dõi cậu để xem có đủ tư cách\N làm chủ nhân của Lilith không,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.73,0:05:10.27,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{and what she likes so much about you.}và tại sao cô ấy lại thích cậu đến vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.90,0:05:16.82,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{First, education.}Đầu tiên là giáo dục.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.82,0:05:20.54,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Let's see if you have the knowledge \Nand sensibility a master should have.}Một chủ nhân cần có kiến thức và sự nhạy cảm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.07,0:05:29.84,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Explain the theory of relativity to me.}Giải thích thuyết tương đối xem nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.70,0:05:32.45,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Sorry, I don't know.}Xin lỗi, tôi không biết.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.89,0:05:35.43,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{You don't even know the \Ntheory of relativity?!}Cậu còn không biết thuyết tương đối?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.68,0:05:37.42,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Do you, Natsume?}Cô biết hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.12,0:05:39.96,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{O-Of course I do.}D-Dĩ nhiên.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.96,0:05:43.47,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{The relatives are, like, y'know, um, stuff.}Đại ý là thế đó, như này này.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.47,0:05:44.65,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{That's the theory.}Lý thuyết là vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.02,0:05:46.57,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{That's impressive.}Ghê nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.11,0:05:52.03,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I don't know about it yet, \Nbut I plan to study it.}Tuy chưa biết nhưng tôi sẽ học.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:54.32,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Yes. I'm sure you will, young master.}Vâng, nếu là chủ nhân...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.65,0:06:06.36,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Just because you're a bit studious doesn't \Nmean you're qualified to be a master.}Chỉ mới học chút ít đừng nghĩ\N mình đã trở thành chủ nhân chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.36,0:06:09.08,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{What's more important is money.}Quan trọng hơn nữa là tiền.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.01,0:06:11.08,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Money...}Tiền...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.58,0:06:13.18,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{That's true.}Đúng là thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:14.37,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Right?}Chứ gì nữa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.37,0:06:16.36,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I don't have money.}Tôi không có tiền.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.59,0:06:19.09,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{You're hopeless.}Thật thất vọng.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.09,0:06:21.94,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{A master has to be able \Nto manage the finances.}Chủ nhân mà không có khả năng quản lý tài chính.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.28,0:06:23.53,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Manage...}Quản lý...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.12,0:06:27.59,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Look at this.}Nhìn xem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.33,0:06:31.98,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I've been saving up a little bit \Nof my allowance each month.}Tôi đã dành dụm từ tiền tiêu vặt hàng tháng đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.09,0:06:34.68,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{That's peanuts.}Chỉ có thế thôi à.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.66,0:06:37.65,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{It's not enough yet,}Vẫn chưa đủ,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:42.26,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{but I hope to get Lilith a \Nfantastic gift with it someday.}nhưng hi vọng ngày nào đó\N có thể mua cho Lilith một món quà.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.16,0:06:44.49,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master...}Chủ nhân...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.08,0:06:50.99,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{I-I have some spending money, too...}T-Tôi cũng có tiền...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.26,0:06:54.28,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{You did love shopping, Natsume.}Cô thích đi mua sắm mà nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.28,0:06:56.92,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I used to come with you all the time.}Tôi thường hay đi chung mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.92,0:06:58.98,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{I prefer to be called a prolific spender!}Tôi thích được gọi là dân chơi hơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:01.50,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{You don't understand anything!}Cô chẳng hiểu gì cả!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.39,0:07:06.30,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,Natsume...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.30,0:07:07.30,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,Cô ổn chứ?{Are you okay?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.69,0:07:09.14,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You should stay back.}Lùi lại đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.14,0:07:10.82,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{There's glass everywhere.}Mảnh vỡ khắp nơi đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.82,0:07:12.24,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I'll go get the broom.}Tôi đi lấy chổi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.24,0:07:14.12,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Thanks, Lilith.}Cảm ơn Lilith.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.16,0:07:16.50,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Are you hurt?}Cô có bị thương không?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.03,0:07:21.29,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{No.}Không.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.60,0:07:23.11,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Thank goodness.}May quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.17,0:07:27.08,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Wh-What's wrong with you?!}C-Cậu bị gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.08,0:07:29.96,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{I just broke something of yours!}Tôi vừa làm vỡ đồ nhà cậu đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.25,0:07:32.33,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,Đâu phải lúc lo cho tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.61,0:07:37.16,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Isn't it normal to be relieved \Nthat no one's hurt?}Lo cho người bị thương là chuyện bình thường mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.16,0:07:38.69,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{B-But...}N-Nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.69,0:07:41.89,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Besides, you're here to see Lilith.}Với cả cô đến gặp Lilith mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.89,0:07:44.59,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I want to treat you like a valued guest.}Bạn của Lilith cũng là của tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.54,0:07:49.57,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Y-You aren't fooling me.}Đ-Đừng có dụ tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.18,0:07:51.47,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Fooling you?}Dụ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:56.81,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Lilith, this kid's deceiving you \Nwith his words, isn't he?}Lilith, cô cũng bị lời nói của cậu ta lừa chứ gì!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.81,0:07:57.40,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.40,0:07:59.59,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{You can't let your guard down \Njust because he's a kid!}Đừng có bất cẩn chỉ vì là con nít!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.59,0:08:02.15,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{There's something wrong with \Nthis master and this mansion!}Cả chủ nhân lẫn căn biệt thự này đều kì lạ!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.15,0:08:05.21,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{I refuse to believe he's your master.}Tôi không tin cậu ta là chủ nhân của cô đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:05.86,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,Natsume,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.52,0:08:10.62,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{please stop speaking ill of my master.}đừng nói xấu chủ nhân của tôi nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.11,0:08:18.99,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{L-Lilith, I'm telling you this for your sake.}L-Lilith, tôi chỉ muốn tốt cho cô thôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.57,0:08:23.13,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{With all due respect, Natsume, \Nthat's what I don't understand.}Natsume, đó mới là điều tôi không hiểu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.49,0:08:26.94,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Why are you so fixated on me?}Tại sao cô cứ cố chấp như thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:33.62,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,Hồi ở học viện cô cũng luôn lại bắt chuyện.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.21,0:08:38.58,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I've troubled you,}Làm phiền tôi,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.41,0:08:42.07,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{and of course, you've done \Nthings for my benefit, too.}dĩ nhiên cô cũng giúp đỡ tôi rất nhiều,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.07,0:08:43.62,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{And you made me happy at times.}và khiến tôi vui vẻ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.23,0:08:46.50,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{And I'm grateful to you for it.}Tôi rất cảm ơn cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:52.40,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{But I'd like you to respect \Nmy will right now.}Nhưng tôi muốn cô tôn trọng cảm xúc của tôi lúc này.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.62,0:08:58.71,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{I'm just looking out for your happiness.}Tôi chỉ muốn cô được hạnh phúc.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.40,0:09:07.88,Flashback - Sus Maid,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Everyone has their own way \Nof expressing their feelings.}Mỗi người đều có cách biểu lộ cảm xúc khác nhau.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:13.08,Flashback - Sus Maid,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Some people even act mean on purpose \Nbecause they can't say they love someone.}Vài người hành động xấu xa\N chỉ vì họ không thể nói lên cảm xúc.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.52,0:09:15.46,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Why would they do that?}Tại sao lại làm thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.46,0:09:19.43,Flashback - Sus Maid,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{That's one of the mysteries of the human heart.}Vì đó là sự bí ẩn của trái tim mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.28,0:09:25.45,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Could it be that you love Lilith, Natsume?}Không lẽ cô thích Lilith à, Natsume?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.70,0:09:29.16,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Huh?!}Hả?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.16,0:09:31.49,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Wh-Wh-What are you talking about?!}T-T-Tại sao cậu lại nói thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.49,0:09:34.32,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Obviously not! That's obviously not it!}Làm gì có chuyện đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.32,0:09:35.89,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Are you sure?}Cô chắc chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.14,0:09:40.26,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You came all the way to this \Nmansion for Lilith's sake.}Cô đường xa lặn lội đến tìm Lilith.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.60,0:09:43.80,Flashback - Sus Maid,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Whatever the reason, \Nstaying here won't do you any good.}Dù lý do là gì, thì cô cũng không nên ở đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.80,0:09:47.89,Flashback - Sus Maid,Natsume,0,0,0,,{You've been on my mind all this time!\NI reached out to you because I care about you!}Tôi luôn nghĩ cho cô, luôn quan tâm đến cô!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.21,0:09:52.38,Flashback - Sus Maid,Natsume,0,0,0,,{I'm just looking out for your happiness.}Tôi chỉ muốn cô được hạnh phúc.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:55.60,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Isn't that because you love her?}Chẳng phải đó là thích sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.60,0:09:57.49,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Wh-Wh-What...}C-C-Cái gì...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.76,0:10:01.80,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I love Lilith.}Tôi yêu Lilith.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.80,0:10:03.84,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{That's why I want her to stay here.}Thế nên muốn cô ấy ở lại.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.84,0:10:04.62,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{What?!}Hả?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.86,0:10:08.10,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You're calling her home \Nbecause you love her, too.}Cô gọi cô ấy về cũng vì cô thích Lilith phải chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:09.51,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Th-That's embarrassing!}X-Xấu hổ quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.51,0:10:11.69,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{How could you say such \Nan embarrassing thing?!}Sao cậu có thể nói ra những điều đó?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.69,0:10:15.61,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Aren't you the least bit \Nembarrassed, even for a child?!}Cậu không có tí xấu hổ nào à?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.96,0:10:19.75,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Is it embarrassing to express your feelings?}Giãi bày cảm xúc thì có gì xấu hổ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.98,0:10:29.90,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{It's embarrassing for people \Nto know how you feel.}Xấu hổ là khi cậu bày tỏ nó với người khác.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:33.01,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{For a grown-up, it's something \Nyou have to hide.}Khi lớn lên, cậu phải tìm cách giấu nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.01,0:10:34.76,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Really?}Thật á?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.79,0:10:37.70,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{But...}Nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:39.32,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I'm in love with you.}Tôi thích cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.65,0:10:41.75,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{How will they know if you don't tell them?}Không nói sao đối phương biết được?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.37,0:10:50.45,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{That's right.}Đúng đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.99,0:10:53.27,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{I love Lilith.}Tôi thích Lilith.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.27,0:10:55.41,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{I can't help but think about her.}Tôi lúc nào cũng nghĩ đến cô ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.23,0:10:57.78,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{I was worried about her.}Tôi luôn lo lắng cho Lilith.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.66,0:11:03.85,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{About what the mansion's like, \Nwhat her master's like, what her life's like,}Về nơi cô ấy ở, chủ nhân của cô ấy, cuộc sống của cô ấy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.12,0:11:06.07,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{if she's happy...}Có hạnh phúc không...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.10,0:11:10.04,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{That's why I came all this way!}Thế nên tôi đã đến đây!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.14,0:11:18.61,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Natsume, I'm sorry for worrying you.}Natsume, xin lỗi vì làm cô lo lắng.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.99,0:11:20.56,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Thank you.}Cảm ơn nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.14,0:11:22.52,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,Lilith...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.52,0:11:25.44,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{But I still don't intend to go home with you.}Nhưng tôi không quay lại đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.63,0:11:30.29,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{S-See? There's nothing good \Nabout saying how you feel!}Q-Quả nhiên thổ lộ cảm xúc chẳng có gì tốt đẹp cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.29,0:11:31.91,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{You tricked me!}Cậu lừa tôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.07,0:11:39.76,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I'm off.}Tôi đi đây!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.71,0:11:43.22,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Off you go, young master.}Chủ nhân đi cẩn thận.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.92,0:11:48.88,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Now...}Giờ thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.06,0:12:04.83,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,Natsume?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.36,0:12:07.54,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{You're a guest.}Cô là khách mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.54,0:12:09.44,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{You don't need to help.}Không cần giúp đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.44,0:12:11.93,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Yeah, but... I mean...}Không... nhưng mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.86,0:12:17.84,Italics,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Back at our mansion, there were \Nseveral maids to do the cleaning.}Ở dinh thự của mình thì có vài người hầu lo dọn dẹp.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:22.47,Italics,Natsume,0,0,0,,{We each had our own posts and specific duties.}Ai cũng có nhiệm vụ riêng.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.04,0:12:26.29,Italics,Natsume,0,0,0,,{We just needed to do what \Nwas assigned to us.}Chỉ cần làm theo chỉ thị là xong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.85,0:12:27.66,Italics,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Fine.}Hiểu rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.45,0:12:32.47,Italics,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Let's see what kind of brutal \Nlabor she's being forced to do.}Để xem cô ấy làm những công việc cực khổ gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.93,0:12:37.39,Italics,Natsume,0,0,0,,{It may be a small mansion, \Nbut there's a lot of area to cover.}Tuy là dinh thự nhỏ nhưng sân vườn cũng lớn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.74,0:12:40.36,Italics,Natsume,0,0,0,,{It must be tough doing it all by herself.}Một mình hẳn rất vất vả.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.02,0:12:44.59,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{You don't have to help, Natsume. \NPlease relax.}Cô cứ thoải mái thôi, đừng cố quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.59,0:12:45.86,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Fine.}Được.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:10.43,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Thank you for your work.}Cô vất vả rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:12.01,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Shall we take a break?}Nghỉ chút nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.01,0:13:14.17,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{I haven't done anything.}Tôi có làm gì đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.71,0:13:16.17,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Aren't you miserable?}Cô không thấy vất vả à?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.56,0:13:19.86,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Working by yourself...}Làm tất cả một mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:24.01,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Isn't it stressful? Tiring? \NDon't you wish you could take a break?}Không khó khăn à? Hay muốn nghỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.01,0:13:25.20,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Not at all.}Không hẳn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.20,0:13:27.02,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{It's for the young master, after all.}Vì tôi làm cho chủ nhân mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.02,0:13:28.73,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{It's nothing.}Nên có là gì đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.96,0:13:32.17,Italics,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Lilith is a diligent person.}Lilith là người rất nghiêm túc.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.17,0:13:35.19,Italics,Natsume,0,0,0,,{I guess the work itself \Nisn't that hard for her.}Với cô ấy thì mấy việc này cũng bình thường.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.38,0:13:39.50,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{The young master should be coming home soon.}Chủ nhân cũng sắp về rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:40.91,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I have to prepare.}Tôi phải đi chuẩn bị.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.04,0:13:43.50,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{H-Hey...}N-Này...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.50,0:13:45.37,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{You haven't rested at all.}Vẫn chưa nghỉ xong mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.15,0:13:49.25,Italics,Natsume,0,0,0,,{The real problem is...}Vấn đề quả nhiên là...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.21,0:13:51.25,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I'm home.}Tôi về rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.25,0:13:52.64,Italics,Natsume,0,0,0,,{...him.}Tên này!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.91,0:13:55.15,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Welcome home, young master.}Mừng ngài đã về.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:13:59.21,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{You're drenched in sweat!}Ngài có vẻ ra mồ hôi nhiều quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.78,0:14:01.06,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Is it because you were...}Không lẽ...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.06,0:14:02.07,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.07,0:14:04.01,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I couldn't wait to see you again.}Tôi muốn được thấy mặt cô nhanh nhất.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.22,0:14:09.98,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{You didn't have to run all the way home.}Ngài không cần phải chạy về đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.98,0:14:11.94,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{You must be tired.}Hẳn đã mệt rồi nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.75,0:14:14.92,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Actually...}Thực ra...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.07,0:14:20.23,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I was thinking about you \Nall day during class.}Tôi đã nghĩ về cô trong suốt giờ học.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.91,0:14:23.38,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,Nghĩ xem cô có mệt mỏi không?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.38,0:14:26.14,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{About what you might be up to right now.}Hay bây giờ cô đang làm gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.88,0:14:31.40,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I got so antsy, I couldn't help but run.}Càng nghĩ càng muốn gặp cô thật nhanh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.96,0:14:37.36,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I love you today, too, Lilith.}Hôm nay tôi cũng thích cô nữa, Lilith!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:46.15,Italics,Natsume,0,0,0,,{This kid's putting Lilith on the spot \Nwith his embarrassing talk again.}Tên nhóc này lại nói mấy câu đáng xấu hổ để ép Lilith!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.15,0:14:49.15,Italics,Natsume,0,0,0,,{No one would know what to say to that!}Ai mà bị nói thế thì chẳng thấy phiền.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.47,0:14:52.69,Italics,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Especially when it's someone \Nso much younger than her!}Đặc biệt là từ một tên nhóc.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.57,0:15:09.05,Italics,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Isn't that right?}Đúng nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.88,0:15:19.46,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Still, I worry that you might trip and \Nhurt yourself, or get in an accident.}Nhưng tôi lo chủ nhân sẽ bị té hay gặp tai nạn lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.84,0:15:23.69,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Please walk home slowly so \Nthat I know you're safe.}Lần sau xin hãy đi từ từ về nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.69,0:15:25.71,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Oh... Okay.}À ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.71,0:15:27.01,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Hello again, Natsume.}Chào cô Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.37,0:15:28.47,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Welcome home.}Mừng cậu về nhà.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.65,0:15:32.39,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{What's the matter, Natsume?}Sao thế Natsume?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.25,0:15:36.63,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{It's nothing.}Không có gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.89,0:15:46.91,Italics,Natsume,0,0,0,,{That's the first time I've \Never seen Lilith like that.}Đây là lần đầu mình thấy Lilith như vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.10,0:15:52.96,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Lilith, I'll help with dinner.}Lilith, tôi phụ nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.96,0:15:54.90,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Thank you.}Cảm ơn chủ nhân.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.90,0:15:59.05,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{But I'm almost done already, \NsoN you don't need to worry about it.}Nhưng tôi sắp xong rồi nên không sao đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.72,0:16:00.89,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Okay.}Vậy à.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.39,0:16:09.80,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Are you really a maid, Natsume?}Cô có thực sự là người hầu không?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.04,0:16:12.02,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{What?! Where did that come from?}Hả? Sao tự nhiên lại?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.02,0:16:16.78,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Well, I can't picture you doing \Nanything that's maid-like.}Thì tôi không nghĩ nổi cô mà lại làm hầu gái...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.78,0:16:18.19,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I haven't seen it, either.}Không tưởng tượng ra luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.68,0:16:21.93,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{And you're eating snacks before dinner.}Và lại còn ăn bánh kẹo trước bữa tối.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.77,0:16:24.73,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{What do snacks have to do with anything?!}Liên quan gì nhau?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.14,0:16:27.26,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Don't you see my clothes?}Không thấy đồng phục à?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.26,0:16:30.33,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{I'm a maid, no matter how you look at it!}Trông thế nào cũng là một hầu gái thực thụ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.29,0:16:34.81,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Is it just for show, then?}Không phải là cosplay à?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.29,0:16:37.19,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Who do you think you are, punk?!}Cậu xem thường tôi à, thằng nhãi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.19,0:16:38.88,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{I'll show you, then!}Vậy thì xem đây!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.88,0:16:39.71,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Watch this!}Tôi sẽ cho cậu thấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.81,0:16:49.80,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{There's nothing to see here!}Không có gì để xem cả!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.80,0:16:51.21,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{You got a problem with me?!}Cậu thích nhìn không?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.74,0:16:56.66,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{As I said before, you're a guest, Natsume.}Tôi đã nói cô là khách rồi mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.66,0:16:58.88,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Please let me take care of the chores.}Để tôi dọn dẹp cho.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.65,0:17:02.74,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You don't have to force \Nyourself if you can't do it.}Không được thì đừng cố quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.42,0:17:06.19,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{I-It's not like I can't.}K-Không phải là không được.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.80,0:17:23.37,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{S-Sorry, Lilith!}X-Xin lỗi Lilith.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.37,0:17:24.56,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Are you all right?}Cô ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.63,0:17:27.04,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{I blew it again.}Tôi lại làm rối tung lên rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.04,0:17:30.49,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Um, um... I need to get \Nsomething to clean this up with.}Tôi... phải tìm đồ lau cho cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.68,0:17:37.31,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Kind of nostalgic, don't you think?}Thật hoài niệm nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.31,0:17:38.76,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Is it?}Vậy à?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.48,0:17:40.27,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Yes.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.68,0:17:43.42,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Natsume was really bad at doing chores.}Natsume rất tệ khoản dọn dẹp.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.42,0:17:48.06,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{She would always mess up, \Nand I would help her each time.}Lúc nào cũng thất bại và tôi đến giúp.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.43,0:18:09.80,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Thanks to that, I've gotten \Ngood at doing chores.}Nhờ thế mà tôi đã trở nên giỏi việc nhà.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:13.53,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{W-Well, sorry!}X-Xin lỗi nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.53,0:18:15.70,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{I can do anything other than chores, though.}Nhưng ngoài việc nhà thì việc gì tôi cũng cân...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.01,0:18:20.67,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{That aside, I think you two \Nshould take a shower.}Cơ mà hai người nên đi tắm đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.67,0:18:22.31,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You're drenched.}Ướt nhẹp rồi kìa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.48,0:18:24.70,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{You're right.}Phải nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.10,0:18:27.17,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{But we haven't cleaned up.}Nhưng vẫn chưa dọn xong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.17,0:18:28.63,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Worry about that later.}Chuyện đó để sau.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.63,0:18:30.63,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You'll smell bad if you stay soaked.}Ướt nhẹp và hôi nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.76,0:18:33.13,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{And you'll catch a cold.}Có thể bị cảm lạnh đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.57,0:18:38.70,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Natsume, would you like \Nto take a bath with me?}Natsume, vào chung không?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.70,0:18:39.50,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Just kidding.}Đùa thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.70,0:18:41.26,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{What?!}Hả?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.26,0:18:42.88,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Who would...}Ai mà thèm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.45,0:18:46.95,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{If you say so.}Nhưng nếu cô nói vậy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.42,0:18:51.68,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{How's the water?}Nước thế nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.11,0:18:53.68,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{It's fine.}Ổn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.73,0:19:01.45,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Natsume, I'm sorry for being \Nso hard on you earlier.}Natsume, xin lỗi vì chuyện lúc nãy nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.40,0:19:09.42,Flashback - Sus Maid,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Please stop speaking ill of my master.}Đừng nói xấu chủ nhân.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.94,0:19:14.39,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{No, I was the one who... you know.}Không... tôi cũng hơi quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.39,0:19:19.56,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{To be honest, I'm relieved that you came.}Nhưng tôi thấy nhẹ nhõm khi cô đến đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.20,0:19:25.44,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{It was a weight off my shoulders.}Cảm giác như thở phào nhẹ nhõm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.85,0:19:28.78,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I think it helped me take my mind off things.}Rũ bỏ mọi suy nghĩ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.48,0:19:36.40,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I don't know how to respond to \Nmy young master's affection.}Vì tôi không biết phải đáp lại\N cảm xúc của chủ nhân như nào...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.34,0:19:43.74,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I never even imagined he would \Nstraight-up tell me he loves me.}Tôi không ngờ ngài ấy lại nói thẳng ra...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.52,0:19:46.69,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{And from the young master I care so much for...}Và chủ nhân cũng quan tâm tôi rất nhiều...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.30,0:19:51.64,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{He hadn't expressed his feelings \Nuntil around the time you arrived.}Trước khi cô đến, chủ nhân \Nkhông bày tỏ cảm xúc của mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.64,0:19:56.42,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Up until then, he was only suspicious of me.}Trước đó chỉ toàn nghi ngờ tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:20:02.39,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{It's all so sudden, I...}Mọi chuyện quá đột ngột... nên tôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.79,0:20:05.26,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I don't know how I feel.}Tôi không biết cảm xúc của mình là thế nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.11,0:20:07.96,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{You don't, huh?}Không biết à?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.49,0:20:16.85,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{You may not have noticed it, \Nbut I figured it out.}Tuy cô chưa nhận ra nhưng tôi biết rõ lắm rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.56,0:20:20.27,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Figured what out?}Biết rõ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.48,0:20:26.01,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{I used to think he was a terrible master,}Tôi đã từng nghĩ cậu ta là chủ nhân tồi tệ,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.01,0:20:31.04,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{tying you down to this dull mansion \Nand troubling you all the time.}trói buộc cô lại nơi này và gây rắc rối cho cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.04,0:20:35.28,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{The face you make when he keeps \Ntelling you he loves you...}Nhưng khuôn mặt cô khi cậu ta bày tỏ cảm xúc...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.41,0:20:37.97,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{You weren't troubled.}Cô chẳng có gì là khó khăn cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.97,0:20:40.21,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{You seemed really happy.}Mà trái lại rất hạnh phúc.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.17,0:20:43.46,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Happy?}Hạnh phúc?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.83,0:20:44.63,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.01,0:20:46.93,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,Nói tóm lại...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.35,0:20:50.90,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{No, that's not for me to say.}Không, tôi không phải người nói.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.90,0:20:53.79,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{That's for you to realize for yourself.}Cô phải tự nhận ra nó chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.19,0:21:02.30,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,Tôi hạnh phúc đến thế sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.30,0:21:03.04,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.04,0:21:05.48,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{You were an open book.}Biểu cảm rõ ràng luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.88,0:21:07.47,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{No...}Không thể nào...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.47,0:21:09.41,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Am I always that way?}Tôi đã luôn như thế sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.70,0:21:12.38,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I'm so embarrassed.}Xấu hổ quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.71,0:21:16.99,Italics,Natsume,0,0,0,,{You looked so happy.}Khuôn mặt hạnh phúc đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.42,0:21:20.61,Italics,Natsume,0,0,0,,{And you started smiling at me, too.}Và cô cũng đã cười với tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.23,0:21:26.21,Italics,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Somehow, that makes me happy, too.}Cảm giác tôi cũng hạnh phúc theo nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.21,0:21:29.15,Italics,Natsume,0,0,0,,{I guess that's also thanks to that little runt.}Có lẽ là nhờ tên nhóc con đó nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.15,0:21:31.01,Italics,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Although I hate to admit it.}Tuy có hơi ghen tị...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:32.63,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You'll catch a cold.}Cô sẽ bị cảm lạnh đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.93,0:21:46.45,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{What were you two talking about \Nin the bath for so long?}Hai người nói gì mà lâu ra thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.57,0:21:50.74,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Grown-up talk.}Chuyện người lớn...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.77,0:21:52.90,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Wha?!}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.96,0:23:31.95,Ep_Title - Sus Maid,Text,0,0,0,,{\an5\blur2\pos(320,250)}{Next Time\NEpisode 10: For Whom Do the Stars Fall}
